item.title: Ok, I have all my no-ip stuff i need and all that now
item.dc:creator: @Ganaray Ganaray
item.description:
@Ganaray wrote:

Search around the forums until you find a link that says ‘Server Status’. Click on it. You will see a list of all the online servers. Scroll all the way down and click on ‘Register Server’. Follow the instructions and fill in everything correctly and your server will be up an running.
